{
  "texts": [
    "Our method can be seamlessly converted to a long video generation model by using an interpolation model [87].Video-LLaVA struggles to capture fine-grained details and often produces irrelevant descriptions that may interfere with prompt instructions.",
    "Consequently, we opt for GPT-4V for video annotation.",
    "Nevertheless, since GPT-4V only processes keyframe inputs rather than entire videos, it risks losing valuable information.",
    "To mitigate this, we introduce Multi-view Text Fusion (MTF) to enhance the quality of video captions.",
    "GPT-4V with MTF can generate text prompts with rich temporal details, object specifics, and narrative coherence."
  ]
}